name: Give Me The Future VR
summary: Journey through the world of Bastille’s “Give Me The Future”, the #1 album inspired by our relationships with technology, lucid dreaming and the coming together of the real and the unreal. Allow Future Inc. to transport you to the Innerverse, where these concepts are brought to life in a stunning virtual reality experience. Explore four songs from the album captured at an exclusive live performance, including a never-seen-before piano version of “No Bad Days” performed by a 20-storey high...
